Description: Web interface for managing Claude Code CLI projects
 Claude Code Web Manager provides a professional web interface for managing
 Claude Code CLI projects on Raspberry Pi.
 .
 Features include:
  * Browser-based terminal interface using TTYd
  * Persistent tmux sessions for continuous development
  * Real-time project management and file operations
  * Monaco Editor integration for code editing
  * WebSocket-based real-time updates
  * Mobile-optimized responsive design
  * System monitoring and status reporting
  * Hardware integration support for Raspberry Pi GPIO
  * Multi-device development continuity
 .
 The application runs as the 'distiller' system user with appropriate
 permissions for hardware access and system integration.
